{"tid":2208073,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★滙豐12月7日起　停滙豐控股及恒生兩股孖展借貸","createTime":"2020-09-18T15:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T13:46:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"90ea806671156fbf8936be9a5dd170c6eb2723b2","tid":2208073,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:07:07.000Z","msg":"滙豐銀行網站顯示，於12月7日起，將終止為滙豐控股(00005)及恒生(00011)兩隻股票提供孖展借貸。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐發言人表示，該行會不定期檢視股票孖展比率。滙豐控股和恒生銀行股票的孖展信貸將於12月7日起終止，建議客戶於3個月通知期內處理投資組合，該行職員將為客戶提供協助<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200918/bkn-20200918213217053-0918_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200918%2Fbkn-20200918213217053-0918_00842_001.html&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=f1e9e5a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200918/bkn-20200918213217053-0918_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b5f3cdca8f0948d82a03a8a22749d71e8b14032","tid":2208073,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcb8228378982f99222779021578d215d96b89a","tid":2208073,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccd72f4751d2d047e81497cd9117df8c1bb4713","tid":2208073,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":